Support

The Anti Adminer can at any time find out if there are crewmates or near Cameras, Admin Table, Vitals, DoorLog and/or other devices.
Note: Anti Adminer does not know for sure if someone is using the device while near it, they only know that someone is near the device.

  • Max
    • Set the Maximum amount of Anti Adminers that can be in a match
  • Can track camera usage
    • : Anti Adminer knows when people are near the cameras
    • : Anti Adminer does not receive this information
